ChatGPT is a conversational Artificial Intelligence model that can generate creative responses to various text-based prompts. It operates sequentially and probabilistically, meaning it can produce different outcomes to the same prompt. The speaker uses the example of asking ChatGPT to write a haiku about the importance of understanding AI. They highlight that the generated responses vary but are insightful in both instances. Internet communities have provided many other examples of interacting with ChatGPT, some of which are compiled and indexed on dedicated websites. These examples showcase the versatility and potential of this AI model in generating text-based content.